{"tid":824673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［下半場］港鐵：東鐵綫及輕鐵綫受損前所未見，暫未知放工時間是否可以全面恢復。","createTime":"2018-09-17T07:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T08:00:38.000Z","uid":49388,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4250f75cdc2548cb288a80fe82ffc273fd0942b6","tid":824673,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"超強颱風吹襲本港後，多處冧樹，港鐵東鐵綫及輕鐵綫只能提供有限度服務。<br />\n<br />\n目前東鐵綫來往大埔至上水的列車服務仍然暫停，另外受路面狀況影響，免費穿梭巴士服務亦未能提供。<br />\n<br />\n其中在粉嶺站需要落閘關閉，有市民鼓譟，不滿港鐵安排，亦有市民認為，今日應該停工。<br />\n<br />\n至於在大圍站，只有一個月台照常運作，乘客迫滿月台及大堂。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，東鐵綫及部分輕鐵綫受損的程度是前所未見，暫時未知放工時間是否可以全面恢復。"},{"pid":"1099b0a3e5f79bafd778ea8143cc0ee59857c1a7","tid":824673,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91abd8c7f79ff1cc3acb8a834d7fabb21bc9bec1","tid":824673,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"食屎啦三條柒"},{"pid":"9e181dfca883e84ce75c50076b109c0f43775888","tid":824673,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"太子站條屎渠好似就快要爆咁"},{"pid":"95d5e243e25e22541f13b49a8ff0818996f9667b","tid":824673,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b65c7b6df9c2d263630c19907df4c950c66dd59","tid":824673,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"老闆: OT O到有車為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33addbf11ebc82d59f1170298778c4bd968a8656","tid":824673,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e181dfca883e84ce75c50076b109c0f43775888","tid":824673,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"太子站條屎渠好似就快要爆咁"},"cit